{"tid":467714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港呢個地方其實都幾靚","createTime":"2017-11-13T17:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T19:20:04.000Z","uid":26020,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6eb96715692caaef736ebe0b5c78436b5a35bc","tid":467714,"uid":26020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:41:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_2quiyHfJQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_2quiyHfJQw&d=4YZ4Yc6MFKezhAiTN64FIP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=9efbe53f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_2quiyHfJQw</a><br />\n啱啱聽完呢隻歌 個mv係香港取景<br />\n平時經過呢啲地方都冇點為意<br />\n雖則說啲招牌可能唔穩陣 霓虹燈光又光污染 <br />\n啲樓又殘又舊 夜晚又成地米奇 <br />\n但唔知點解都好鍾意呢啲地方 點都好撚過周街商場 各色各樣   <br />\n如果我係外地人嚟香港都會去呢啲地方 <br />\n香港特色 要好好保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd157212a8786920995296527fb78f8687cb9c0","tid":467714,"uid":26020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:00:54.000Z","msg":"偽文青 文化沙漠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc863b82b374e0f9d2470983a40a6d02595ef8f","tid":467714,"uid":146728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2i2khp_npdE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2i2khp_npdE&d=4YZ4Yc6MFKezhAiTN64FIP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=64d71985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2i2khp_npdE</a><br />\n<br />\nmy favourite <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c647ffb50cb8fab5b17d4d6759fbe16194f21378","tid":467714,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:34:55.000Z","msg":"用到濫哂啦個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c6afb57a82b5e552518e7fcc8b1c1347e3cb53","tid":467714,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor